<h2>
Hello

I bring you my new pretab which i am using my my map surf_CTH. This is very detailed arrows and very big so it will fit into any map. 

<hr />

More Info On Prefabs :

[1] I did NOT use any custom textures.
[2] The blue one is a Enlargement of a laser texture.
[3] The gray one is An Enlargement of a DEV texture
[4] Easy to edit and make your own shape.
[5] Very big arrows, made for surf map but you can resize.
[6] All In A .WMF Hammer file.
[7] No player have been added.
[8] Made 100% by me.

<font color="green">Note: The Arrow's Are B I G ! Made for any size of map.</font>

<hr />

Average Mapping Time : 1H and 10m
Average Compile Time : 19s

<hr />

<font color="red">Sorry About My Spelling. :]</font>
